item.title: Better Living Through Chemicals
item.description: Freestyler’s Anonymous (FA) Callback from KZSU that’s what my dad said he wants to do 3 applications of roundup in the way back and ironically there were 2 commercials of the monsanto class acttion lawsuit stuff saying to call if you’ve been exposed to chemicals. so I’m not about it. hate it. hate it hate it all and everyone’s gone an dI just need to record my albums and my mood is gone .
